list.abstract: Exchange （Exchange Server） 是一个设计完备的邮件服务器产品，提供了通常所需要的全部邮件服务功能。简单而言，Exchange server可以被用来构架应用于企业、学校的邮件系统甚至于像sohu或sina那样的免费邮件系统。 Exchange server还是一个协作平台。可以在此基础上开发工作流、知识管理系统、Web系统或者是其他消息系统。除了常规的 SMTP/POP 协议服务之外，它还支持 IMAP4 、LDAP 和 NNTP 协议。Exchange Server 服务器有两种版本，标准版包括 Active Server、网络新闻服务和一系列与其他邮件系统的接口；企业版除了包括标准版的功能外，还包括与 IBM OfficeVision、X.400、VM 和 SNADS 通信的电子邮件网关，Exchange Server 支持基于Web 浏览器的邮件访问。

yingyinNormal.en: How is the soft power exchange between these two roommates?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这两个室友之间的软实力交换情况怎样呢？

yingyinNormal.en: They exchange a thousand bits of information between them per second.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每秒可以交换一千位的信息。

yingyinNormal.en: And I also want to impress upon all of you here today the importance of that soft culture, that soft power exchange, and how each of us is involved in that exchange.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天在这里，我还要向你们强调软文化，软实力，交换的重要性，以及我们每个人都逃不开这场交换。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Hi. You, ready to exchange gifts? Sure. Okay, you go first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以交换礼物了吗？当然，你先。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you say we exchange gifts? Oh, Sheldon, we didn't bring any.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们开始交换礼物吧？谢尔顿，我们没带礼物啊。

yingyinNormal.en: And that this exchange needs to have a healthy balance. And how do we address this?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种交换需要健康的平衡，如何解决呢？

yingyinNormal.en: But in exchange, I'd like you to do a few things for me. What kinds of things?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，你要为我做几件事作为交换。什么事？

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. Isn't it ironic that David would show up on the same day that you and Mike exchange keys?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大卫出现在你跟麦克交换钥匙的同一天，这真是很讽刺。

yingyinNormal.en: When I thought you wanted sex in exchange for this job, I said no. That shows integrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我以为你要我用性来交换工作，当时我拒绝了，这表示我有骨气。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't come to Oxford as an exchange student from Taiwan and only hang out with other Chinese students.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个学生从台湾到牛津来交换，不要只和中国学生一起。

yingyinNormal.en: So, I'm gonna need to have that back. But, in exchange I'm willing to trade you this beautiful, more expensive ring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过我愿意拿这枚美丽的，更昂贵的戒指和你交换。

yingyinNormal.en: How about this. I work for you and in exchange, you teach me how to clean? What do you think?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样好不好，我为你工作，作为交换，你教我怎么杀人，你觉得怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, Nemo. Who's this? Exchange student. I'm from the E.A.C., dude! Sweet! Totally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好, 尼莫，这是谁? 交换生，我是顺着东澳洋流来的朋友! 真可爱! 没错。

yingyinNormal.en: And a consortium of American and Chinese energy companies tackles the remaining 20%, in exchange for which they get drilling rights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个美中能源企业的联盟解决剩下的20%，我们以开采权作为交换。

yingyinNormal.en: If a potential mate has managed to pass all these tests, there's still one more: the infamous first kiss, a rich and complex exchange of tactile and chemical cues, such as the smell of one's breath, and the taste of their mouth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果有某个可能的对象通过这些检验，最后还有一项：恶名昭彰的初吻，初吻交换丰富而复杂的触觉及化学信号，像是呼吸的气味及嘴巴的味道。

yingyinNormal.en: A whole world and exchange for a statue. Gods are strange creatures.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一尊雕像换来一整个世界，神真是奇怪的生物。

yingyinNormal.en: They were just giving those away at the store, in exchange for money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是唱片行的赠品，我得拿钱去换。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the exchange rate? None of your business. Take it or leave it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 汇率是多少？不关你事。成还不成？

yingyinNormal.en: When did you last eat? When did you last eat? currency exchange? You know, food.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你上次就餐是什么时候？还有对货币兑换所造成的影响？我指的是食物。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. I need you to tell me about the drug exchange. One of you must've seen something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你们得告诉我毒品交易的事，你俩肯定有人看到了什么。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an act of giving one thing and receiving another in return, especially of the same type or value

examination_example.sentence: Labour is provided free in <highlight>exchange</highlight> for the hope of status.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 劳动力是免费提供的，以换取地位的希望。

examination_example.sentence: "There seems to be a predominance of short-term thinking at the expense of long-term investing," said Commissioner Daniel Gallagher of <highlight>Exchange</highlight> Commission.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国交易委员会委员丹尼尔•加拉格尔表示:“短期思维似乎占据了主导地位，损害了长期投资。”

sense_info_list.en: a visit or visits in which two people or groups from different countries stay with each other or do each other's jobs

examination_example.sentence: We readjust our view of arguments—from a verbal fight to a reasoned <highlight>exchange</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们重新调整对争论的看法——从口头上的争吵到理性的交流。

examination_example.sentence: Verbal expressions are unnecessary for emotional <highlight>exchange</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 语言表达在情感交流中是不必要的。

examination_example.sentence: However, Obamacare has allowed more than 12 million people to either get insurance through Medicaid or the <highlight>exchanges</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，奥巴马医改已经允许超过1200万人通过医疗补助计划或医保交易所获得保险。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an act of giving one thing and receiving another in return, especially of the same type or value

examination_example.sentence: Billions of people use social media on a daily basis to create, share, and <highlight>exchange</highlight> ideas, messages, and information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数十亿人每天都在使用社交媒体来创建、分享和交换想法、消息和信息。

examination_example.sentence: They don't <highlight>exchange</highlight> ideas, they <highlight>exchange</highlight> images.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们不交换想法，他们交换图像。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>exchange</highlight>, he guarantees an above-market price for each animal and a calf-to-customer electronic ear tag ID system like that used in the European Union.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为交换，他保证每只动物的价格都高于市场价，并且提供从小牛到客户的电子耳标 ID 系统（如欧盟使用的系统）。

sense_info_list.en: a visit or visits in which two people or groups from different countries stay with each other or do each other's jobs

examination_example.sentence: He deplored that broadcasting had become a one-way means of communication and foresaw it moving in another direction, toward communication as a means of <highlight>exchange</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他对广播已经成为一种单向的交流方式表示遗憾，并预见到广播将朝着另一个方向发展，成为一种交流方式。

examination_example.sentence: Promote its cultural <highlight>exchange</highlight> with other nations.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 促进与其他国家的文化交流。

examination_example.sentence: Probing the rock pools of a local beach or practising French on a language <highlight>exchange</highlight> can fire children's passions, boost their skills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在当地海滩的岩石池里探索，或者通过语言交流练习法语，都可以激发孩子们的热情，提高他们的技能。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an act of giving one thing and receiving another in return, especially of the same type or value

examination_example.sentence: On August 5, the number of postcards <highlight>exchanged</highlight> by members topped 31 million.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 8月5日，会员交换明信片数量突破3100万张。

examination_example.sentence: Information was <highlight>exchanged</highlight>, but it wasn't a true, intentional back and forth.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然信息交换了，但不是一场真实的，有意的交流。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 交换学生；交流学生；交换生

examination_example.sentence: As an <highlight>exchange</highlight> student, I studied in France for two years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为交换生，我在法国学习了两年。

examination_example.sentence: China and the US should have another table tennis <highlight>exchange</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 中国和美国应该再进行一次乒乓球交流。

examination_example.sentence: I'm having a great time on my student <highlight>exchange</highlight> program here.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我在这里的学生交流项目中过得很愉快。

examination_example.sentence: Tom had <highlight>exchanged</highlight> the next turn with Billy Fisher for a good kite.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 汤姆通过和比利·费希尔交换了下一个回合的机会，换到了一只好风筝。

examination_example.sentence: Galileo knew Copernicus and <highlight>exchanged</highlight> letters with him.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 伽利略认识哥白尼，并与他交换信件。

examination_example.sentence: It was a good way to <highlight>exchange</highlight> language and culture.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是交流语言和文化的好方法。

examination_example.sentence: We have set some ground rules that my daughter must follow in <highlight>exchange</highlight> for us providing a phone.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们制定了一些基本规则，我女儿必须遵守，作为交换，我们提供一部手机。

examination_example.sentence: Alibaba went public on the New York Stock <highlight>Exchange</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 阿里巴巴在纽约证券交易所上市。
